s/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一開始係會肚餓，堅持下去個胃就會習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，我一開始都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，吃蘋果抵肚餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"393c84279f929fcedc8042a89ff4828a07c3629d","tid":482443,"uid":40297,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T08:19:07.000Z","msg":"4個月42磅。餐餐都飽 <br />\n早餐 麥皮 水果 蛋<br />\n中午 晚餐 半碗飯 3-4條雞柳/蒸新牛肉 菜<br />\n3日gym 3-4日跑步/急行 1hr <br />\n有時4點會餓就食多隻蛋<br />\n星期日有時會食煎牛排/中意食既野（謝絕油炸/甜食/零食）"},{"pid":"992b75195c4a1dd42a2347c96351968f822dbab7","tid":482443,"uid":22999,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T08:19:30.000Z","msg":"冬天特別易肥，因為打得邊爐多同個人易肚餓，減肥係一場長期戰爭，加油啊，巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，要記住堅持就是勝利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"158d6ac6de35778f3b3d3bd2ccaec2444adb7062","tid":482443,"uid":78770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T08:34:36.000Z","msg":"想問下大家一開始點會堅持到每日/隔日去做運動?<br />\n上星期慢跑左4日 40mins<br />\n今個星期完全冇動力去做"},{"pid":"0c7da38c8d0c4f3d71af041c0289f608d549a756","tid":482443,"uid":33389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T08:36:48.000Z","msg":"我想要增肥法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食量比其他人多一半都愈食愈瘦"},{"pid":"a1584c180763b5822478e77810c91f4c0c842078","tid":482443,"uid":42676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T08:46:35.000Z","msg":"不如巴絲分享一下唔運動淨係靠飲食既減肥例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c6f69d356a5b51bc710562827bc4f79cf0b8be3","tid":482443,"uid":97136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T08:56:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下大家一開始點會堅持到每日/隔日去做運動?<br />\n上星期慢跑左4日 40mins<br />\n今個星期完全冇動力去做</blockquote><br />\n我之前一個星期跑 3~4日到<br />\n都係靠frd一齊分享下成績<br />\n擺上ig鼓勵下自己咁<br />\n半年瘦左5kg左右 <br />\n無咩點戒口 食多左菜 飲多左水 少啲飲有味野咁囉"},{"pid":"2d6c662863e7430f1b75c5b3307358c2755f956a","tid":482443,"uid":78770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T09:06:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想問下大家一開始點會堅持到每日/隔日去做運動?<br />\n上星期慢跑左4日 40mins<br />\n今個星期完全冇動力去做</blockquote><br />\n我之前一個星期跑 3~4日到<br />\n都係靠frd一齊分享下成績<br />\n擺上ig鼓勵下自己咁<br />\n半年瘦左5kg左右 <br />\n無咩點戒口 食多左菜 飲多左水 少啲飲有味野咁囉</blockquote><br />\n巴打第一個月減左幾多?<br />\n我目標係2月尾要減到10kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec70b88aa094a6bc94b46ea19707df06c367e574","tid":482443,"uid":156331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T09:09:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"62822199b2a4949e2c13273dbe5b228b4ef5ae2f","tid":482443,"uid":22999,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T09:45:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不如巴絲分享一下唔運動淨係靠飲食既減肥例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇特登運動，靠戒甜同節食瘦咗20磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：好懶做運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c803a1d94e7c168cafa4ac0d433772f8a87c39a","tid":482443,"uid":46018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T10:01:03.000Z","msg":"3年幾，減左30幾kg，90幾kg到60Kg<br />\n前前後後有平台期各樣<br />\n而家有隔日做gym同跑步<br />\n飲食而家就食蛋白質為主，有蛋，奶，豆漿，雞胸，麥皮，香蕉，吞拿魚....<br />\n碳水就通粉，麥包<br />\n我自己會日日煮野食，就算返工都帶飯<br />\n 戒曬零食，煮野唔落油，唔落醬，可能落d鹽（不過而家懶到用水煮熟就算）"},{"pid":"b08d23910751e86a24978fff1a1a0c56b1331d7b","tid":482443,"uid":42676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T11:15:47.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96a4867a6a59055c8b87ba5e9f25f3046341073d","tid":482443,"uid":135445,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T12:55:06.000Z","msg":"Don&rsquo;t always being crazy la<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown